Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:39.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates  who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after \NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in \Nthe turmoil and involved in an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:04:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Hordy's merciless plot puts the \NFish-Man Island in unprecedented danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My axe! Hit Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fish-Man Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:44.97,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Luffy Loses the Fight?! \NHordy's Long-Awaited Revenge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's dead finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Vander Decken's \Npower became ineffective
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Noah will crash \Ninto the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all those people who stand \Nin the way of our vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Fish-Man Island...\N--...Will be no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to stop the ship somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna stop the Noah, don't \Nyou? Then you have to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you can't save \Nthe Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Noah crashes into the Fish-Man \NIsland, it will be the end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the kingdom and the Noah's purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that has been protected \Nfor hundreds of years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, my sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ark - the Noah is not just  \Na relic from history-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hundreds of years ago, a promise \Nwas made to a great man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that ship has been kept on the \Nseafloor until the appointed day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has not served \Nits purpose yet-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we don't even know \Nhow they made that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Noah cannot be damaged \Nuntil the day comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will go and find out why \Nit moved and take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save both the kingdom \Nand the Noah at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you have neither \Na strategy to stop the Noah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor a chance to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? If nothing is done,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your friends will have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to be swallowed by the sea, \Nalong with the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you fooling yourself when you said \Nyou'd protect them all, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna break it to pieces \Nbefore it gets to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that, Straw Hat! \NEven if you could do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I told you, the Noah has
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a long history and will serve \Na purpose in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how can we save the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can think of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken could still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can wake him up, maybe we \Ncan change the course of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he's dead? Then what are \Nwe gonna do? We gotta destroy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys splitting? While you're arguing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look, the Noah is falling towards the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Noah! There are people \Nwho I love on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decken-sama! If you are alive, \Nplease make it come after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't harm the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead now and watch it from beyond \Nthe grave, as the Ryugu Kingdom falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Drums!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Mamboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can defend myself \Nwith the Armament Haki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my Haki is not good enough \Nfor these kind of attacks yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't be fighting in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to beat him, I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to fight on the \Nfalling ship, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what he really wants is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the air on its deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could get in there, I can \Nbeat Hordy with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew he was going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bubbles are susceptible \Nto large gashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The air on the deck is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy to render you humans helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should realize you're \Nno better than us Fish-Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only can you not stop the \NNoah but you can't even beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snake Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm stupid enough \Nto get hit by the same attack twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which comes first - your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being shattered to death \Nalong with the island
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or your last breath! Can't wait to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He's gonna break my bubble again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dullard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to handle Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handle Luffy-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop Hordy at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust me no matter what \Nhappens and stay close to the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens! Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can miss now! \NEven with my eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama asked me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy! What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many lives on \Nthat island! How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three Princes are the \Nstrongest in the Ryugu Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you are sons \Nof that stupid Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no pride in being a \NFish-Man and died a dog's death
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to become friendly with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are worthless Princes who \Ncan't even save your own country!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your power is fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I admit that I couldn't fight back \Nbecause I'm not strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merman Combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultramarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me with \Nthose crappy attacks now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Hordy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you want \Nbadly enough to sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so many innocent fellowmen's lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do such a horrible thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy! Ultra...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic, you piss-poor Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is a gift from heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me with that fake power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy, what's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You petitioned for vengeance against \Nthe humans to Fish-Men, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're trying to take those fellow \NFish-Men's lives along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even abandoned the ones you grew \Nup with in the Fish-Man District!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you realize what you are doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is your hatred for humans so \Ndeep that makes you lose your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did humans beat you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did humans kill your loved \Nones or someone dear to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you go through in the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did humans do to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi! Brother-hoshi \Nis in trouble! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Hey! Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Yowahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust me no matter what \Nhappens and stay close to the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens! Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy-san, this is the \NAir Tank. We met you a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.14,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,AIR TANK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been listening to what's \Nbeen going on out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we see the Noah falling \Ntowards the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:09.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,CONTROL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting ready as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Brother-hoshi was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go to the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go after him!\N--No, wait, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy has an advantage in the \Nwater since he is a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If nothing is done...\N--What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.49,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?! Brother-hoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:48.35,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MAIN ENTRANCE OF THE FISH-MAN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought you here, Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we might need a \Nlarge amount of air soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. There is some air on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can beat him up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from Decken,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think Hordy would leave the \Nbubble so you can fight there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take this Baby \NTransponder Snail just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be well-prepared. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama! What should I do about the Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Fukaboshi-sama told me \Nto stay close to the Noah along
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Luffy-sama, no matter what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what Brother-hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, hello?  How can we get air from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can shoot all the air from the Air Tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the Air Tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an air conditioning facility that's \Nproviding air to the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make a bubble and shoot it, \Nmaybe we can surround the Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bubbles neutralize ascending forces
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not going to make the Noah float.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can't stop it from falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, we have to use all the air
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe have in order to engulf that giant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there is only one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't shoot it at the exact moment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthat the Noah comes right beside us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be no second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, it's a hit-or-miss situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. And I'm afraid you'll \Nhave to take it from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I can't emphasize enough that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the difficult \Nstuff and just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle anything \Nas long as there is air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, please save the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can they accomplish by \Nswimming alongside the Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are only a human and a Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting up quite a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Human! Give it up, Human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick to my stomach \Njust looking at you people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it shortens my life and even \Nif it comes at the ultimate price,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will execute my revenge on you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss it! You don't \Nhave a second chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss it, the \NFish-Man Island will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Brother Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother-hoshi, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barely alive. Anyway, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Hordy Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out who he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Noah once again draws near,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Island is in chaos \Nas the citizens evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats continue to \Nbelieve in Luffy and fight on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune's army finally \Njoins the battle, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle at the Conchcorde \NPlaza is unfolding rapidly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a new truth further \Nshakes up the citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Shocking Fact! The \NTrue Identity of Hordy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
